{"tid":624012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小學大食會經歷","createTime":"2018-04-10T12:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T14:48:37.000Z","uid":41229,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"044110592ea201941e91f6d8477c81e64c15b54c","tid":624012,"uid":41229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:34:03.000Z","msg":"見到飲食台個小食po唸起小學大食會<br />\n老母買左包餅仔比我帶返學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到大食會個陣人人都雞翼,波羅腸仔,魚蛋燒賣之類<br />\n然後就見到其他同學異樣嘅目光同偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個刻我覺得自己好似個異類咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係要怪屋企窮<br />\n但點解負擔唔起仲要生我出黎<br />\n<br />\n利申 有能力前唔會生，唔想禍害下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/202612_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F202612_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=7ff18d14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd62e26dd4ff333ce6e5b063bf1dce0933af804d","tid":624012,"uid":41229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人有類似經歷分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea55d44e767fd11a940cbf9735add9aa71bb0e8","tid":624012,"uid":107656,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"你share你包餅<br />\n但係就食菠蘿腸仔魚蛋燒賣<br />\n伯母幾識計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86455e08ba88b5e42b9b5cf65ae20b228efb17b4","tid":624012,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa4a1f94a697e85b368a2e8a53ce678731e55149","tid":624012,"uid":41229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你share你包餅<br />\n但係就食菠蘿腸仔魚蛋燒賣<br />\n伯母幾識計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔好意思食人地d野<br />\n最尾匿埋食自己包餅算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0382bdd63e3b99e19881f85bf8021e15a519703","tid":624012,"uid":41229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我帶開花膠同鮑魚 d人追住我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打真係幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6aec5934562428942c5d0aef581c396aa154a7","tid":624012,"uid":169231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86455e08ba88b5e42b9b5cf65ae20b228efb17b4","tid":624012,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"追住食鮑魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3c86f2b42d5ef4e69403d8398c4c6ca688a47f","tid":624012,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小學老母會俾十幾廿蚊我買堆零食番去"},{"pid":"2a685b28e8d8959e488a0a55a264c2b4e29a6e71","tid":624012,"uid":89476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"有一次小學大食會<br />\n<br />\n老母比左兩包時時食我番去<br />\n<br />\n人地擺出黎成台都係大包薯片乜都有<br />\n<br />\n我偷偷地將果兩包餅放係d薯片後面<br />\n<br />\n就去食下其他野<br />\n<br />\n到完果時我發覺果兩包餅開左<br />\n<br />\n但係原來一塊都冇人食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119a87956104aac91f007f85f2163ceff70b2154","tid":624012,"uid":41229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一次小學大食會<br />\n<br />\n老母比左兩包時時食我番去<br />\n<br />\n人地擺出黎成台都係大包薯片乜都有<br />\n<br />\n我偷偷地將果兩包餅放係d薯片後面<br />\n<br />\n就去食下其他野<br />\n<br />\n到完果時我發覺果兩包餅開左<br />\n<br />\n但係原來一塊都冇人食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條友開左唔食個下賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f329665df1be5ff05661ac7240d79167c3c78d3","tid":624012,"uid":41229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我帶開花膠同鮑魚 d人追住我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>追住食鮑魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n腸仔食唔食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}